INSERT INTO `category_translations` VALUES (6,'Root','root','Root',NULL,'','','',1,'en',NULL,''),(7,'Raz','root','Raz',NULL,'','','',1,'es',NULL,''),(8,'Racine','root','Racine',NULL,'','','',1,'fr',NULL,''),(9,'Hoofdcategorie','root','Hoofdcategorie',NULL,'','','',1,'nl',NULL,''),(10,'Kk','root','Kk',NULL,'','','',1,'tr',NULL,''),(11,'Mobility','mobility','<p>Our mobility is our ability to move around freely &ndash; for many people who face mobility limitations, through illness, injury, aging or disability, that freedom is often taken away. Mobility aids are important pieces of durable medical equipment (DME) to not only reduce the pain associated with movement, butalso to help improve the independence of those with mobility limitationsand increase their access to the world.</p>','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">cura360 has a wide range of DME solutions, and our team of experts can help you find the right medicalequipment available for your needs, and your budget. We have manual wheelchairs, power wheelchairs, mobility scooters, wheelchair cushions, canes, crutches, walkers and rollators, wheelchair batteries, scooter batteries, lift chairs, power adapters, vehicle lifts, patient lifts and more from leading DME brands, all with a price match guarantee.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If mobility is an ongoing issue for you, a loved one, or a patient, now might be the time to purchase a mobility aid from cura360. It is always worth getting advice from a medical professional on the right solution to your mobility problem &ndash; whether it is a short-term solution to pain or discomfort, or an injury to overcome, or a long-term solution to improve your quality of life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Speak to one of our experts now on 1-833-207-3433 for for advice on choosing the right solution for you &ndash; or check out our network of local care professionals for a medical opinion.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>','','','',2,'en',1,'mobility'),(16,'Manual Wheelchairs','manual-wheelchairs','<p>Manual Wheelchairs are defined as wheelchairs that require a person to move the chair from place to place.</p>','<p>Manual Wheelchairs are defined as wheelchairs that require a person to move the chair from place to place. A transport wheelchair requires an attendant to move but many typical manual wheelchairs can be pushed by either an attendant or the occupant. Some other common types of manual wheelchairs include folding, rigid, lightweight, and ultra-lightweight, shower, beach, standing, reclining, and tilt-in-space. There are available some power options on some manual wheelchairs, such as the Smart Drive &reg; power assist to help push a manual wheelchair, and there are some standing wheelchairs that feature a motorized lift feature, but still require the occupant to move the chair from place to place on their own.</p>','','','',3,'en',1,'manual-wheelchairs'),(21,'Rehab and Braces','rehab-and-braces','<p>Rehab and Braces</p>','','','','',4,'en',1,'rehab-and-braces'),(26,'Respiratory','respiratory','<p>Respiratory</p>','','','','',5,'en',1,'respiratory'),(31,'Women Health','women-health','<p>Women Health</p>','','','','',6,'en',1,'women-health'),(36,'Urological','urological','<p>Urological</p>','','','','',7,'en',1,'urological'),(41,'Incontinence','incontinence','<p>Incontinence</p>','','','','',8,'en',1,'incontinence'),(46,'Ostomy','ostomy','<p>Ostomy</p>','','','','',9,'en',1,'ostomy'),(51,'Wound Care','wound-care','<p>Wound Care</p>','','','','',10,'en',1,'manual-wheelchairs/basic-wheelchairs-transport-chairs-and-transformer-chairs/wound-care'),(56,'Power Wheelchairs','power-wheelchairs','<p>Cura360 has a low-price guarantee and a wide selection of power wheelchairs, so you are sure to find the perfect power solution for you. Power scooters and power wheelchairs differ in that Scooters are entered from the side and steer manually with a handlebar while power chairs are typically entered from the front and steer with a joy/control stick. Power wheelchairs are often referred to as electric wheelchairs. You will find power options for travel that fit in the trunk of your car for long-range with a variety of speeds, even elevating power wheelchairs that help you reach higher heights.</p>','<p>Allowing those with little strength and stamina to travel distances with ease. Power wheelchairs feature a variety of design types; from travel chairs to heavy-duty models and mid, front, and rear-wheel drive types. This variety allows for greater use in different scenarios or terrain. The sophistication in the controls allows for ease of use with those having limited hand dexterity. Power chairs offer a great turning radius for indoor use and around tight spaces. With Power Chairs take very little effort to use, it is a good idea to have a supplemental exercise program available along with a good cushion to prevent muscle breakdown.</p>\r\n<p>Cura360 has a large selection of Powerchairs and electric chairs, wheelchairs that can be of great help to restore your mobility</p>','','','',11,'en',1,'power-wheelchairs'),(65,'Mobility Scooters','mobility-scooters','<p>A mobility scooter is an electrically powered mobility aid that is designed to look like a scooter. A Mobility Scooter is a three-wheeled or four-wheeled vehicle with a rechargeable battery, often known as a power-operated vehicle (POV). These models are designed for persons who have difficulty walking or getting around but do not require the assistance of a power wheelchair. Mobility scooters are portable and convenient because they are easy to assemble and disassemble. At Cura360, we have a wide range of Mobility Scooters to choose from. If you need help deciding, read the helpful information below, or call our experts at&nbsp;1-833-207-3433</p>','<p>Choosing a Mobility Scooter at first might be somewhat precarious.</p>\r\n<p>Cura360.com allows isolated users, who lack transport or have limited mobility, to continue accessing the best life-enhancing medical products and services while regaining their independence.</p>\r\n<p>Our digital marketplace (Cura360.com) offers a wide selection of affordable DME products like Mobility Scooters from the leading manufacturers in the country. Mobility Scooters is one of our main highlighted products amongst many others. Cura360 aims to provide greater access for all. Customers no longer have to leave their homes to get the medical advice, equipment and services they need for their rehabilitation.</p>','','','',16,'en',NULL,'mobility-scooters'),(66,'Wheelchair Cushion & Seating','wheelchair-cushion-seating','<p>Wheelchair Cushion &amp; Seating</p>','<p>Wheelchair Cushion &amp; Seating</p>','','','',17,'en',NULL,'mobility/wheelchair-cushion-seating'),(67,'Walking Aids','walking-aids','<p>Walking Aids</p>','<p>Walking Aids</p>','','','',18,'en',NULL,'mobility/walking-aids'),(68,'Wheelchair Accessories','wheelchair-accessories','<p>Wheelchair Accessories</p>','<p>Wheelchair Accessories</p>','','','',19,'en',NULL,'mobility/wheelchair-accessories'),(69,'Lift Chairs','lift-chairs','<p>Lift Chairs</p>','<p>Lift Chairs</p>','','','',20,'en',NULL,'mobility/lift-chairs'),(70,'Vehicle Lifts','vehicle-lifts','<p>Vehicle Lifts</p>','<p>Vehicle Lifts</p>','','','',21,'en',NULL,'mobility/vehicle-lifts'),(71,'Braces and Compression','braces-and-compression','<p>Braces and Compression</p>','<p>Braces and Compression</p>','','','',22,'en',NULL,'rehab-and-braces/braces-and-compression'),(72,'Rehab and Therapy','rehab-and-therapy','<p>Rehab and Therapy</p>','<p>Rehab and Therapy</p>','','','',23,'en',NULL,'rehab-and-braces/rehab-and-therapy'),(73,'Medical Furniture','medical-furniture','<p>Medical Furniture</p>','<p>Medical Furniture</p>','','','',24,'en',NULL,'medical-furniture'),(74,'Beds','beds','<p>Beds</p>','<p>Beds</p>','','','',25,'en',NULL,'medical-furniture/beds'),(75,'Chairs','chairs','<p>Chairs</p>','<p>Chairs</p>','','','',26,'en',NULL,'medi