looking for a manual wheelchair to reduce or prevent upper-body mobility-related injuries skip down to our therapeutic wheelchair section.</p>\r\n<h2>What are the different types of Manual Wheelchairs?</h2>\r\n<p>There are several types of manual wheelchairs available for different types of users. The first and most important question is whether the person in the chair is going to be exclusively propelled by others, self-propelled by the user, or a combination of both. If you&rsquo;re looking for a manual wheelchair to reduce or prevent upper body mobility-related injuries skip down to our therapeutic wheelchair section.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','','',36,'en',NULL,'manual-wheelchairs/basic-wheelchairs-transport-chairs-and-transformer-chairs'),(86,'Travel Folding Mobility scooters','travel-folding-mobility-scooters','<p>Travel Folding Mobility scooters</p>','<p>Travel Folding Mobility scooters</p>','','','',37,'en',NULL,'mobility-scooters/travel-folding-mobility-scooters'),(87,'Mobility Scooter Mid-Sized','mobility-scooter-mid-sized','<p>Mobility Scooter Mid-Sized</p>','<p>Mobility Scooter Mid-Sized</p>','','','',38,'en',NULL,'mobility-scooters/mobility-scooter-mid-sized'),(88,'Mobility Scooter Full Sized','mobility-scooter-full-sized','<p>Mobility Scooter Full Sized</p>','<p>Mobility Scooter Full Sized</p>','','','',39,'en',NULL,'mobility-scooters/mobility-scooter-full-sized'),(89,'Heavy Duty/ High weight capacity mobility Scooters','heavy-duty-high-weight-capacity-mobility-scooters','<p>Heavy Duty/ High weight capacity mobility Scooters</p>','<p>Heavy Duty/ High weight capacity mobility Scooters</p>','','','',40,'en',NULL,'mobility-scooters/heavy-duty-high-weight-capacity-mobility-scooters'),(90,'All-Terrain Scooter','all-terrain-scooter','<p>All-Terrain Scooter</p>','<p>All-Terrain Scooter</p>','','','',41,'en',NULL,'mobility-scooters/all-terrain-scooter'),(91,'Electric Bikes','electric-bikes','<p>Electric Bikes</p>','<p>Electric Bikes</p>','','','',42,'en',NULL,'