INSERT INTO `product_attribute_values` VALUES (7522,'en','default','<p>Foldawheel PW-1000XL weighs only 25.5 kg (56 lb) and it takes just 1 second to open/fold. It is a slightly wider version of our lightest power wheelchair PW-999UL, and it is built for heavier load capacity. If you love to drive a bit faster and need a bit more seat space, this would be an excellent choice. 2 years International warranty and Travel Bag as an optional accessory. The price you pay for now comes with 2 batteries.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,9),(7523,'en','default','<p>Lightweight Power Wheelchair &ndash; Foldawheel PW-1000XL is a wider version of our well-known model PW-999UL, it is more powerful, faster with a longer driving range.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Important features of PW-1000XL:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Opens and Folds in just 1 second and fit easily in the trunk of a small car. (Some users can swing it to open/fold with one hand). Stands upright by itself after folded and you can roll it with wheels.</li>\r\n<li>Foldawheel PW-1000XL lightweight power wheelchair is only 25.5 kg (56 lb) if without battery. And each battery weighs just 1.7 kg (3.7 lb). The price you pay for now comes with 2 batteries. (Total weight 63.5 lb)</li>\r\n<li>Each battery can operate about 15km (9.3 miles), and the standard delivery comes with 2 batteries to operate about 30km (18.6 miles), which should be more than enough for most users. The travel range of 25km was tested with a user at 100kg (220lb) on a usual flat surface environment.</li>\r\n<li>You can also add one extra battery upon placing the order to travel nearly 45km (28 miles). The battery compartment can hold up to 3 batteries.</li>\r\n<li>The weight capacity is 150 kg (330 lb), but don&rsquo;t worry if you exceed a bit more because it has a very sturdy structure.</li>\r\n<li>Equipped with safer and more durable Soft Pack Polymer Li-ion cells (similar to iPad or Macbook except it is bigger capacity).</li>\r\n<li>5-speed control and the joystick serve as the accelerator. Maximum speed up to 8 km/hr (5 miles/hr) with 10&Prime; rear wheels.</li>\r\n<li>The 2 powerful 250W brushless motors produce higher torque and more energy-saving compares to the traditional brush motors.</li>\r\n<li>High-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy frame for stronger, safer, and more durable.</li>\r\n<li>Detachable seat cushion and backrest for washing purposes.</li>\r\n<li>Both armrests can be raised up to get closer to tables or easier transfer to other surfaces</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Other special features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Equipped with 4 spring suspensions for more comfort on bumpy rides.</li>\r\n<li>The latest joystick controller is smaller and easier to control. You can remove it conveniently with the detachable cable system upon check-in the power chair as luggage.</li>\r\n<li>Detachable seat cushion and washable seat cover.</li>\r\n<li>Detachable anti-tilt support is provided (the user should install it for safety or without it if the usage environment is always on a flat surface).</li>\r\n<li>Detachable anti-tilt support is provided (the user should install it for safety or without it if the usage environment is always on a flat surface).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,10),(7524,NULL,NULL,'FWPW-1000XL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,1),(7525,'en','default','Foldawheel PW-1000XL Lightweight Folding Power Wheelchair',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,2),(7526,NULL,NULL,'foldawheel-pw-1000xl-lightweight-folding-power-wheelchair',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,3),(7527,NULL,'default',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,4),(7528,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,5),(7529,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,6),(7530,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,7),(7531,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,8),(7532,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,38,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,25),(7533,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,26),(7534,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,27),(7535,NULL,NULL,'<p>Foldawheel Series Lloyd Standing Series, PW-4x4Q. The warranty for the above wheelchair models is up to &ldquo;5 years Limited International Warranty&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 102px;\" width=\"332\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">Parts</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">Warranty Duration (years)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">Wheelchair Frame</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">Motor and Controller</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">2</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">Battery</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 158.6px;\">1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>The following are not covered under this warranty: Backrest and seat cushion, armrest pad, Storage/Travel Bags.</p>\r\n<p>The warranty only covers NON-DELIVBERATE OR NON-ACCIDENTAL damage. Damage caused by user negligence, accidental damage, intentional or not, are not covered under this warranty. Products which have been subjected to negligence, abuse, improper storage, improper handling or operation, any modification or misuse are not covered by this warranty. Any damage caused by improper usage, or normal wear and tear is not covered, and you should not use this warranty claim. If you are sure you need to file a warranty claim, please provide as much information as you can about the issue.</p>\r\n<p>Upon warranty claim, we will ask for photos of the chair to verify its condition. If photos cannot be provided, warranty parts will not be provided. Kingly provide photos of your wheelchair upon claiming any warranty, especially if it involves the motors or frame. There is no exception to this policy.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,31),(7536,NULL,NULL,'<p>There are no returns on Foldawheel products.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,362,33),(7537,'en','default','',NULL,NULL