</li>\r\n<li>We use high-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy to make a more robust, safer, and more durable frame.</li>\r\n<li>The armrests can be raised for easier transfer or to get closer to tables.</li>\r\n<li>The unique inward folding footrest is robust and allows users to have the nearest stand-up / sit-down position.</li>\r\n<li>The widest part of the chair is only 23.5&Prime;; therefore, it is to pass through very narrow passages</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2em; color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong>The System:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2em; color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Turning at the slope is now possible with the latest control system.</li>\r\n<li>The speed going down slopes can be under control; it will not increase velocity due to gravity.</li>\r\n<li>Going straight across a slanted path walk is easy too.</li>\r\n<li>The latest joystick controller is easy to control. You can remove it conveniently with the detachable cable system upon check-in the power chair as luggage.</li>\r\n<li>5-speed control and the joystick serve as the accelerator. Maximum speed up to 6.5 km/hr (4 miles/hr) with 8&Prime; rear wheels.</li>\r\n<li>The 2 powerful brushless motors provide higher torque and more energy-saving than traditional brush motors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>The Battery:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Battery packs are inside the side panel, and it is easy to pull out.</li>\r\n<li>We use high-quality Li-ion cells to make the battery packs safer and more durable.</li>\r\n<li>The price you pay is Foldawheel PW-999UL with 2 batteries.</li>\r\n<li>Travels up to 32km (20 miles) with a full charge (Tested with a user of 200 lb on a flat surface environment.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Other Unique Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The seat cushion and backrest cover material Air-Breeze is a non-fray material that allows more airflow and a better cushioning effect. It is more durable and detachable for washing purposes.</li>\r\n<li>Patented anti-tilt support with a hydraulic system. It folds in when the chair is folded and comes out when open.</li>\r\n<li>The thick padded travel bag is an excellent optional accessory to ensure no surprise after getting down from the plane.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>What else comes with this Lightest Power Chair PW-999UL?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A good quality certified smart 3A Charger (100V-230V), so you can use it anywhere in the world.</li>\r\n<li>Up to 5 years Global Warranty (It doesn&rsquo;t matter where you travel).</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,10),(7552,NULL,NULL,'FWPW-999UL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,1),(7553,'en','default','Foldawheel PW-999UL Folding Power Wheelchair',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,2),(7554,NULL,NULL,'foldawheel-pw-999ul-folding-power-wheelchair',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,3),(7555,NULL,'default',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,4),(7556,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,5),(7557,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,364,6),(7558,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,