top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">An item must first be returned and received before an exchange or refund is processed</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. </span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; line-height: 1.2;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If a return is not received by the carrier within 15 days after the request has been approved we will consider the item as not returned and a refund will not be processed, or we will have to charge for the cost of the replacement sent to the customer.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A return must be authorized by our support team in order to be eligible for a return. Troubleshooting MUST be done before authorizing a return/exchange/replacement.&nbsp; </span>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 6.5pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-siz