erit; font-size: 1.75rem;\">Features</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"clearfix\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">SMOOTHLY NAVIGATE ANY SURFACE</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Featuring powerful motors, front shock absorbers, and solid tires to easily navigate over grass, gravel, pavement, carpeting&nbsp;&amp; other hard surfaces</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">SIMPLE FOLDING DESIGN</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Folding in seconds, the power wheelchair is ideal for air travel, cruise ship travel and similar outings</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">EASY TO OPERATE</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Repositionable, 360-degree joystick controller + includes battery charge indicator, horn, speed controls&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;USB charging port</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">POWERFUL DUAL MOTORS</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Powered by a rechargeable battery, with a maximum speed of 3.7 mph and a driving distance up to 6.2 miles per charge</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">DURABLE FRAME</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Constructed with lightweight aluminum,&nbsp;to safely support up to 260 pounds and includes adjustable footrest, armrests and seat back height</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">CUSHIONED SEATING</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Generously padded with a dense foam, the 17.5&rdquo; wide seat is covered with soft, breathable material for optimal comfort and includes an adjustable safety belt</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"reviews_422593168\" class=\"spr-reviews\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #212529; font-size: 1.75rem;\">FAQ</h2>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 1.3125rem;\">How do I set-up the Vive Power Wheelchair?</h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 1.3125rem;\">Does the power wheelchair have a neutral/manual mode in case the battery dies while we are out?</h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Yes! The power wheelchair can be placed in manual mode by turning the levels located behind each rear wheel. Do not operate the wheelchair in manual mode alone.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 1.3125rem;\">Is the footrest adjustable?</h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Yes, the footrest can be adjusted to rest in two positions by removing the bolts and reassembling in the new position.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bo