ty to adjust the max speed for added safety. A mounted basket is also included.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Fitting</h3>\r\n<p>The Model C2 can be easily adjusted from seat height and back support angle to controller position (right or left drive) to create a comfortable driving experience.</p>\r\n<div><header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Specifications</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Driving Range</td>\r\n<td>11 Miles</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Maximum Speed</td>\r\n<td>5 MPH</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Max Incline</td>\r\n<td>10&deg;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Obstacle Clearance</td>\r\n<td>2&Prime;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Turning Radius</td>\r\n<td>29.9&Prime;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Seat Sizes Available</td>\r\n<td>16&Prime;/18&Prime;/20&Prime;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Device Width</td>\r\n<td>21.8&Prime;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Device Length</td>\r\n<td>38.8&Prime;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Weight Fully Assembled</td>\r\n<td>114 lbs</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Suspension</td>\r\n<td>4 Wheel Independent</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Charge Time</td>\r\n<td>~ 5 hours</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>App Enabled</td>\r\n<td>Yes, with remote control</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Air Travel Approved</td>\r\n<td>Yes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Swappable Arm Covers</td>\r\n<td>6 Colors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Weight Capacity</td>\r\n<td>Up to 300 lbs</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Battery</td>\r\n<td>Li-ion /6 Ibs</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Weather Tested</td>\r\n<td>IPX4</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;16\" x 16\" - Weight Cap 250lbs - total length including footplate 38.8\" - Total width 22\"</p>\r\n<p>18\" x 18\" -&nbsp;Weight Cap 300lbs - total length including footplate 38.8\" - Total width 23.6\"</p>\r\n<p>20\" x 18\" - Weight&nbsp;Cap 300lbs - total length including footplate 38.8\" - Tota