INSERT INTO `product_flat` VALUES (362,'FWPW-1000XL','','Foldawheel PW-1000XL Lightweight Folding Power Wheelchair','<p>Lightweight Power Wheelchair &ndash; Foldawheel PW-1000XL is a wider version of our well-known model PW-999UL, it is more powerful, faster with a longer driving range.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Important features of PW-1000XL:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Opens and Folds in just 1 second and fit easily in the trunk of a small car. (Some users can swing it to open/fold with one hand). Stands upright by itself after folded and you can roll it with wheels.</li>\r\n<li>Foldawheel PW-1000XL lightweight power wheelchair is only 25.5 kg (56 lb) if without battery. And each battery weighs just 1.7 kg (3.7 lb). The price you pay for now comes with 2 batteries. (Total weight 63.5 lb)</li>\r\n<li>Each battery can operate about 15km (9.3 miles), and the standard delivery comes with 2 batteries to operate about 30km (18.6 miles), which should be more than enough for most users. The travel range of 25km was tested with a user at 100kg (220lb) on a usual flat surface environment.</li>\r\n<li>You can also add one extra battery upon placing the order to travel nearly 45km (28 miles). The battery compartment can hold up to 3 batteries.</li>\r\n<li>The weight capacity is 150 kg (330 lb), but don&rsquo;t worry if you exceed a bit more because it has a very sturdy structure.</li>\r\n<li>Equipped with safer and more durable Soft Pack Polymer Li-ion cells (similar to iPad or Macbook except it is bigger capacity).</li>\r\n<li>5-speed control and the joystick serve as the accelerator. Maximum speed up to 8 km/hr (5 miles/hr) with 10&Prime; rear wheels.</li>\r\n<li>The 2 powerful 250W brushless motors produce higher torque and more energy-saving compares to the traditional brush motors.</li>\r\n<li>High-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy frame for stronger, safer, and more durable.</li>\r\n<li>Detachable seat cushion and backrest for washing purposes.</li>\r\n<li>Both armrests can be raised up to get closer to tables or easier transfer to other surfaces</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Other special features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Equipped with 4 spring suspensions for more comfort on bumpy rides.</li>\r\n<li>The latest joystick controller is smaller and easier to control. You can remove it conveniently with the detachable cable system upon check-in the power chair as luggage.</li>\r\n<li>Detachable seat cushion and washable seat cover.</li>\r\n<li>Detachable anti-tilt support is provided (the user should install it for safety or without it if the usage environment is always on a flat surface).</li>\r\n<li>Detachable anti-tilt support is provided (the user should install it for safety or without it if the usage environment is always on a flat surface).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','foldawheel-pw-1000xl-lightweight-folding-power-wheelchair',1,1,1,NULL,2400.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,330.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 16:02:52','en','default',362,'2022-09-12 16:38:19',NULL,1,2400.0000,2400.0000,'<p>Foldawheel PW-1000XL weighs only 25.5 kg (56 lb) and it takes just 1 second to open/fold. It is a slightly wider version of our lightest power wheelchair PW-999UL, and it is built for heavier load capacity. If you love to drive a bit faster and need a bit more seat space, this would be an excellent choice. 2 years International warranty and Travel Bag as an optional accessory. The price you pay for now comes with 2 batteries.</p>','','','',0.0000,0.0000,NULL,38,'Foldawheel','<p>There are no returns on Foldawheel products.</p>','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(364,'FWPW-999UL','','Foldawheel PW-999UL Folding Power Wheelchair','<p>Foldawheel PW-999UL was the first portable power chair globally, and the first version started in 2012. We have been making improvements yearly, and it has proven to be the most reliable, durable &amp; user-friendly power chair, with more than 10,000 happy users worldwide.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The Product:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>This lightest power chair weighs 20.4 kg (45 lb) without the battery, and each additional battery weighs only 1.5 kg (3.3 lb).</li>\r\n<li>It can open / fold in just 1 second and fits easily in the trunk of a small car.</li>\r\n<li>The weight capacity of Foldawheel PW-999UL is 100 kg (220 lb) (It is strong enough for a much heavier weight, but sitting comfort is another concern). For bigger users, we suggest PW-1000XL.</li>\r\n<li>We use high-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy to make a more robust, safer, and more durable frame.</li>\r\n<li>The armrests can be raised for easier transfer or to get closer to tables.</li>\r\n<li>The unique inward folding footrest is robust and allows users to have the nearest stand-up / sit-down position.</li>\r\n<li>The widest part of the chair is only 23.5&Prime;; therefore, it is to pass through very narrow passages</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2em; color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong>The System:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2em; color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Turning at the slope is now possible with the latest control system.</li>\r\n<li>The speed going down slopes can be under control; it will not increase velocity due to gravity.</li>\r\n<li>Going straight across a slanted path walk is easy too.</li>\r\n<li>The latest joystick controller is easy to control. You can remove it conveniently with the detachable cable system upon check-in the power chair as luggage.</li>\r\n<li>5-speed control and the joystick serve as the accelerator. Maximum speed up to 6.5 km/hr (4 miles/hr) with 8&Prime; rear wheels.</li>\r\n<li>The 2 powerful brushless motors provide higher torque and more energy-saving than traditional brush motors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>The Battery:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Battery packs are inside the side panel, and it is easy to pull out.</li>\r\n<li>We use high-quality Li-ion cells to make the battery packs safer and more durable.</li>\r\n<li>The price you pay is Foldawheel PW-999UL with 2 batteries.</li>\r\n<li>Travels up to 32km (20 miles) with a full charge (Tested with a user of 200 lb on a flat surface environment.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Other Unique Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The seat cushion and backrest cover material Air-Breeze is a non-fray material that allows more airflow and a better cushioning effect. It is more durable and detachable for washing purposes.</li>\r\n<li>Patented anti-tilt support with a hydraulic system. It folds in when the chair is folded and comes out when open.</li>\r\n<li>The thick padded travel bag is an excellent optional accessory to ensure no surprise after getting down from the plane.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>What else comes with this Lightest Power Chair PW-999UL?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A good quality certified smart 3A Charger (100V-230V), so you can use it anywhere in the world.</li>\r\n<li>Up to 5 years Global Warranty (It doesn&rsquo;t matter where you travel).</li>\r\n</ul>','foldawheel-pw-999ul-folding-power-wheelchair',1,1,1,NULL,2199.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,45.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 16:38:43','en','default',364,'2022-09-12 16:38:43',NULL,1,2199.0000,2199.0000,'<p>PW-999UL is the lightest power chair in the world</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>This latest version comes with special system.</li>\r\n<li>Travels up to 32 km (20 miles) with a full charge.</li>\r\n<li>Open / Fold in only 1 second, fits in any car trunk.</li>\r\n<li>Total width of 23.5&Prime; allows you to pass through very narrow passages.</li>\r\n<li>2 batteries + up to 5 years international warranty.</li>\r\n</ul>','','','',0.0000,0.0000,NULL,38,'Foldawheel','<p>There are no returns on Foldawheel products.</p>','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(365,'FW-Leo','','Foldawheel Leo Lightweight Manual Standing Wheelchair','<p><strong>Leo is the best and lightest standing wheelchair:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Leo is the Lightest Standing Wheelchair, and it has changed the lives of uncountable users worldwide. The results and convenience are so much better than the conventional standing frame/standing bed, primarily if you actively use it as exercise &amp; rehab aid equipment.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cura360.com//storage/tinymce/gExCMpOHJzd5t943I7fErdy5qxuVtX1St24DE48S.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"214\" /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Leo provides you with 10 health benefits, convenience, better exercise, and it can even improve your work capabilities.</li>\r\n<li>With a proprietary user-controlled stand-sit mechanism, the user can control the stand or sit movement at his own pace to prevent muscle spasms.</li>\r\n<li>Practise stand up, sit down frequently, and stand as long as possible for maximum health benefits.</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>It is suitable for paraplegia with good strength in arms, palms, and fingers. (Otherwise, Pegasus would be the alternate choice. Should you want to move in standing position, please look into Phoenix and Draco)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Daily life Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>Many users enjoy using Leo portable standing wheelchair to start their exercise life in a regular gym.</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>Leo also enhances their working and study capabilities, including cooking, teaching, daily office work, including presentations.</li>\r\n<li></li>\r\n<li>Social life becomes more manageable when standing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Unique Features of Leo Standing Wheelchair:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Very safe, and no worries of falling forward due to our patented mechanism. (And our standing wheelchairs has been sold in the market for many years with an excellent reputation)</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable seat depth &amp; footrest height to suit users of different sizes and leg lengths.</li>\r\n<li>You may use your cushion on the seat because the seat is velcro ready.</li>\r\n<li>It is equipped with Rear Wheels Suspension by Polyurethane blocks to provide more comfortable rides.</li>\r\n<li>The footrest angle is adjustable to stretch the calf muscles and tendons as the user stands up.</li>\r\n<li>Quick-release front and rear wheels with a foldable backrest to become a very compact size so that it can fit in a regular car trunk.</li>\r\n<li>Total weight at only 27 kg (59 lb) and can reduce to 21.5 kg (47 lb) after detaching the 4 wheels by quick-release function.</li>\r\n<li>Uses only high-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy to ensure lightweight, durability, and safety standards.</li>\r\n<li>Available in 14&Prime;, 16&Prime;, 18&Prime; seat width with multiple adjustable parts to suit different body sizes.</li>\r\n<li>It comes with different straps for the knee, ankle, chest, and safety belt. (Optional safety features like thigh strap and H-shape harness are available too).</li>\r\n<li>Up to 5-years international warranty</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Leo Standing Wheelchair vs other standing equipment:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Regular active wheelchairs can&rsquo;t give you the health benefits and convenience like Leo.</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Leo braces your knees and stretches your tendons much better than the standing frame and standing bed.</span></li>\r\n<li>Effectively prevents pressure sore under the feet as the user can conveniently sit down frequently anytime.</li>\r\n<li>Be more independent when it comes to standing/sitting or changing positions of pressure points.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Remarks:</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Many users call it Leo 2 Standing Wheelchair or just Leo II Wheelchair because it is the 2nd generation of our model Leo.</li>\r\n<li>If you are looking for standing wheelchairs for sale or the lightest standing wheelchair, Leo II Standing Wheelchair is the best recommended manual standing wheelchair in the market.</li>\r\n<li>Lots of spinal cord injury paraplegia depend on our products in their daily lives and exercises, which speaks for quality and usability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','foldawheel-leo-lightweight-manual-standing-wheelchair',1,1,1,NULL,3300.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,59.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 17:03:20','en','default',365,'2022-09-12 17:03:20',NULL,1,3300.0000,3300.0000,'<p>Leo is the only standing wheelchair that is stylish, lightweight, durable, and user-friendly. Its also known as the lightest standing wheelchair in the world. Leo is your best choice if you enjoy using a manual wheelchair and would like to stand up by yourself frequently. It also fits easily in a car trunk.</p>\r\n<p>It is scientifically proven that frequent stand-up can prevent and improve health problems associated with &ldquo;long periods of wheelchair sitting,&rdquo; including bedsore, skin breakdown, poor blood circulation, muscle spasms, and tendon shrinkage. Standing can also help you improve bone density, urinary health, bowel movement etc.</p>\r\n<p>Have you thought of exercising and working in a standing position? Please check out the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1LUsvxQKVf4\">video</a> to see how good it is.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;A simple mechinical lift system allows the patient to use their arms to lift to the standing position safetly and securely.</p>','','','',0.0000,0.0000,NULL,38,'Foldawheel','<p>Thare are no returns allowed on Foldawheel products.</p>','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(366,'FW-Pegasus','','Foldawheel Pegasus Powered Lift Standing Manual Wheelchair','<p><strong>Pegasus: Semi-Power Standing wheelchair</strong></p>\r\n<p>If you like the idea of our standing wheelchair Leo, but lacks the strength from palms and fingers, you can use Pegasus. You need to use one finger to control the stand/sit movement.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cura360.com//storage/tinymce/UBSBpj2nFK5mvswnLYXzVjgebl7rDC1f5veD656f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"214\" /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pegasus has a similar function as Leo but with the power stand/sit function. You can control Up/Down movement at your own pace with a small controller at the tip of the armrest.</li>\r\n<li>It is suitable for paraplegia and hemiplegia users with weak arms, hands &amp; fingers. (Should you want to drive or travel in a standing position, kindly look into the fully powered models Phoenix and Draco).</li>\r\n<li>Practise stand up and sit down frequently for maximum health benefits. Great to serve as a physiotherapy equipment for home, hospital, or rehab center.</li>\r\n<li>Both front and rear wheels are quick-release detachable, with solid PU tires.</li>\r\n<li>You can detach the 4 wheels and then fold down the backrest to become compact enough to fit in a regular car trunk.</li>\r\n<li>Total weight of this semi-power standing wheelchair is 32kg (70.4 lb), however, can reduce to 27kg (59.4 lb) after detaching 4 wheels by quick-release function.</li>\r\n<li>Uses only high-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy to ensure lightweight, durability, and safety standards.</li>\r\n<li>Pegasus is available in 14&Prime;, 16&Prime;, 18&Prime; seat width with multiple adjustable parts to suit different body sizes.</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable seat depth &amp; footrest height to suit users with different sizes and leg lengths.</li>\r\n<li>The footrest angle is adjustable to stretch the calf muscles and tendons as the user stands up.</li>\r\n<li>It comes with other straps for the knee, chest, and safety belt. (In addition, optional safety straps like thigh strap, ankle strap, H-shape harness are available too).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Other Important Features of Pegasus Semi-Power Standing Wheelchair</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>It is equipped with Rear Wheels Suspension by Polyurethane blocks in order to provide more comfortable rides.</li>\r\n<li>You may use your cushion on the seat because the seat is velcro ready.</li>\r\n<li>Up to 5-year international warranty</li>\r\n</ul>','foldawheel-pegasus-powered-lift-standing-manual-wheelchair',1,1,1,NULL,4800.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,70.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 17:28:29','en','default',366,'2022-09-12 17:28:29',NULL,1,4800.0000,4800.0000,'<p>Pegasus is suitable for users with weak fingers, palms, and arms. It allows you to stand-up or sit down by a simple power control function while the chair is self-propelled like any other manual wheelchair. Frequently standing up can significantly improve the user&rsquo;s health and prevent problems due to extended sitting. Great to serve as a physiotherapy equipment for home, hospital, or rehab center. The up/down position can control by a small, easy to use, swtich at the tip of the armrest.</p>\r\n<p>See a video <a href=\"https://youtu.be/oYWTpYqiCOQ\">here</a>.</p>','','','',0.0000,0.0000,NULL,38,'Foldawheel','<p>Thare are no returns allowed on Foldawheel products.</p>','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(367,'FW-Phoenix','','Foldawheel Phoenix Fully Powered Standing Wheelchair','<p><strong>Phoenix &ndash; Power Standing Wheelchair</strong></p>\r\n<p>Phoenix allows you to stand, sit, and move in a standing position and it also provides you the priceless 10 health benefits.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cura360.com//storage/tinymce/GwIh16cX6GazWnAR9BnqpiV9P64ayoBSUmGAd0mV.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"214\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Phoenix is so worthy &amp; valuable?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>This Phoenix power wheelchair enables the user to move in a standing position, stand and sit in steady and safe movement.</li>\r\n<li>5-speed control with driving speed up to 8km/hr (5 miles/hr).</li>\r\n<li>Travels up to 30km (18.5 miles) with a full charge.</li>\r\n<li>Equipped with Dynamic Shark Controller system for precise user control and sensors for safety.</li>\r\n<li>Automatically adjust to slow speed during non-sitting position for safety.</li>\r\n<li>The backrest is reclinable 25 degrees to maximize comfort.</li>\r\n<li>Equipped with LED lights for night going out and signal warning purposes.</li>\r\n<li>Available in 14&Prime;, 16&Prime;, 18&Prime; seat width with multiple adjustable parts, hence can suit different body sizes.</li>\r\n<li>Different types of straps for knee, calves, chest, and safety belt for safety and comfort.</li>\r\n<li>Optional thigh strap, ankle strap, H-shape harness are available upon request too.</li>\r\n<li>Safety is always our No.1 priority while we designed the stylish structure. Only high-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy is used to ensure durability and safety standards.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Other Important Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The footrest angle is adjustable to stretch the calf muscles and tendons as the user stands up.</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable seat depth &amp; footrest height to suit users with different height and leg length.</li>\r\n<li>3-layers foam cushion and back support to ensure extra comfort.</li>\r\n<li>Rear spring suspension for extra comfort over rough terrains.</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable and removable headrest.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Remarks:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Phoenix is an excellent power sit to stand power wheelchair plus 25-degree recline function.</li>\r\n<li>Some user may call it Phoenix 2 or Phoenix II, because this is the 2nd generation of Phoenix.</li>\r\n<li>Travel distance may vary depends on how many times the user stands up /down, slopes to pass through and user weight etc).</li>\r\n<li>If you are looking for a more functional power standing wheelchair, you may look into our Draco.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','foldawheel-phoenix-fully-powered-standing-wheelchair',1,1,1,NULL,7800.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 17:45:04','en','default',367,'2022-09-12 17:45:04',NULL,1,7800.0000,7800.0000,'<p>Phoenix is the latest model power-standing wheelchair on the market. You can move in the standing position and recline 25 degrees for more comfort. It comes with full specifications including an adjustable headrest, H-shape harness for safety, and LED light for nightime independance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','','',0.0000,0.0000,NULL,38,'Foldawheel','<p>Thare are no returns allowed on Foldawheel products.</p>','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(368,'FW-Draco','','Foldawheel Draco Multi-Function Standing Power Wheelchair','<p><strong>Draco &ndash; The Best Power Standing Wheelchair:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Draco is the most functional standing wheelchair out of all the models, excellent for users:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>With easily swelling feet (especially users with diabetes).</li>\r\n<li>Require to take a few naps in the day.</li>\r\n<li>Need extra comfort throughout the day.</li>\r\n<li>Want to constantly change the positions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cura360.com//storage/tinymce/9GJBpCu8qdLrS4uYjUlcN39e58sxGKsZ2IRdjwSc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"214\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Important Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fully powered for lie down, stand, sit and recline positions. It also allows you to move in a standing position.</li>\r\n<li>8 wheels to provide excellent stability especially when the user lies down.</li>\r\n<li>5-speed control with driving speed up to 8km/hr (5 miles/hr).</li>\r\n<li>Travels up to 30km (18.5 miles) with a full charge.</li>\r\n<li>Equipped with Dynamic LED graphic display Controller (DX2) for precise user control and sensors for safety.</li>\r\n<li>Automatically adjust to slow speed during standing or recline position for safety.</li>\r\n<li>Motorized wheels are located in the center to ensure a tight turning radius.</li>\r\n<li>Available in 14&Prime;, 16&Prime;, 18&Prime; seat width with multiple adjustable parts to suit different body sizes.</li>\r\n<li>The footrest, armrest, and backrest move in a coordinated way simultaneously, so the user will not feel the muscle pull when changing from standing &ndash; sit &ndash; lie down position.</li>\r\n<li>Comes with different types of straps for knee, calve, chest and safety belt. (Optional thigh strap, ankle strap, H-shape harness are available too).</li>\r\n<li>Safety is always our No.1 priority when we designed this stylish structure, and only high-grade aircraft quality aluminum alloy is used to ensure durability and safety standards.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Other Unique Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The footrest angle is adjustable to stretch the calf muscles and tendons as the user stands up.</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable seat depth &amp; footrest height to suit users with different height and leg length.</li>\r\n<li>3-layers foam cushion and back support to ensure extra comfort.</li>\r\n<li>Spring suspension for extra comfort over rough terrains.</li>\r\n<li>Adjustable and removable headrest.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Remarks</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>If you are looking for a lay down wheelchair that is the most functional electric standing wheelchair, Draco definitely is your best choice.</li>\r\n<li>But if you don&rsquo;t need lay down function or raise up the legs, then Phoenix would be your ideal motorized wheelchair</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','foldawheel-draco-multi-function-standing-power-wheelchair',1,1,1,NULL,9900.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,30.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 18:04:22','en','default',368,'2022-09-12 18:04:22',NULL,1,9900.0000,9900.0000,'<p>Draco standing wheelchair is the best power standing wheelchair thats equiped with full function capability allows you to move, stand, sit, recline and lie down in safe and comfortable positions. With Draco, you can minimize the risk and effort of transferring users during the daytime as users can take a nap in a lie-down position. The Draco is the only Foldawheel Standing Power wheelchair that allows you full moblity while in the standing position.</p>\r\n<p>Check out this <a href=\"https://youtu.be/sd4SzCAuXC0\">video </a>for more info.</p>','','','',0.0000,0.0000,NULL,38,'Foldawheel','<p>There are no returns available for Foldawheel products.</p>','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(369,'FW-PW-4x4Q','','Foldawheel PW-4x4Q All Terrain Stair Climbing Heavy Duty Power Wheelchair','<p><strong>All-Terrain Recreational Vehicle (PW-4x4Q)</strong></p>\r\n<p>There are many obstacles outside, especially if you are active and enjoy outdoor activities. PW-4x4Q is an all-terrain recreational vehicle that can help you overcome most of the environments you might encounter outdoor (For instance steps, snow, steep slopes, sandy beach, muddy or bumpy roads etc).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Main Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The Gyro System automatically adjusts the seat angle which allows your body to maintain an upright position during stairs climbing or at slopes. It also enabled the seat to power tilt-in-space for more comfort.</li>\r\n<li>It can climb up and down the stairs as high as 15cm (6&Prime;) at 25 degrees.</li>\r\n<li>PW-4x4Q is a 4-Wheel drive system (4WD) for all-terrain purposes.</li>\r\n<li>When traveling on a flat surface, you can operate with only 3 wheels to save electricity. (Just drop the 5th wheel and engage it to work with the 2 front wheels together).</li>\r\n<li>It can travel up to 24km (15 miles) with 3 wheels and 18km (11 miles) with 4WD. Assuming the user weighs 75KG (165 lb)</li>\r\n<li>The top driving speed is 7km/hr (4.35 mph)</li>\r\n<li>Uses Li-ion Batteries (More durable and efficient vs. the traditional Lead Acid Batteries)</li>\r\n<li>Able to make a 360&deg; U-turn on the spot, with a turning radius of only 123cm (48.4&Prime;).</li>\r\n<li>Front, rear, and side LED lights are obvious while driving on the road at night.</li>\r\n<li>The raisable armrest is height and width adjustable&nbsp; (can adjust between 50-59cm wide).</li>\r\n<li>2nd user can stand behind the seat to travel together.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Latest improvement vs the previous model.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Lower seat level for more effortless transfer and better stability.</li>\r\n<li>Using the latest Dynamic controller for better control precision, stability, and comfort.</li>\r\n<li>The 5th wheel is now at a new position with a better structure to ensure energy-savings and durability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Remarks:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Optional extra-wide tires are available for snow and beach environment.</li>\r\n<li>Optional Detachable rear seat</li>\r\n<li>Most users that purchased this PW-4x4Q also own either our Foldawheel PW-999UL or Leo</li>\r\n<li>Please feel free to contact us for more details on this wonderful PW-4x4Q.</li>\r\n</ul>','foldawheel-pw-4x4q-all-terrain-stair-climbing-heavy-duty-power-wheelchair',1,1,1,NULL,12900.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,165.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2022-09-12 18:53:31','en','default',369,'2022-09-12 18:53:31',NULL,1,12900.0000,12900.0000,'<p>The Foldawheel PW-4x4Q is an All-Terrain Recreational Vehicle with all-terrain capabilities. It has 4-Wheel Drive &amp; a seat aligning Gyro system that can handle rugged terrain including steep slopes, snow, sandy beaches, muddy or bumpy roads etc. while keeping your weight right over the wheels for maximum safety and confidence. With its unique gyro balance system, the PW-4x4Q can also climb outdoor stairs* and curbs with a breeeze. Let the PW-4x4Q help you to&nbsp; enjoy destinations previously out of reach.</p>\r\n<p>Check out this <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/686208828?embedded=true&amp;source=vimeo_logo&amp;owner=49390125\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">video </a>to see the PW in action.</p>\r\n<p>This product is not a medical device.</p>\r\n<p>*stair climbing has height and slope limitations.</p>','','','',0.0000,0.0000,NULL,38,'Foldawheel','<p>There are no returns on Foldawheel products.</p>','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(370,'EW-M31','','EW-M31 Compact Power Wheelchair','<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Seat Width 18.5&rdquo;Top Speed 4 mph</p>\r\n<p>Adjustable Headrest</p>\r\n<p>Drive Range 15.2 miles</p>\r\n<p>Weight Capacity 300 lbs</p>\r\n<p>Indoor/Outdoor</p>\r\n<p>General Specifications:</p>\r\n<p>Swing-Away joystick: Yes</p>\r\n<p>Lap Belt: Yes</p>\r\n<p>Variable Speed Dial: Yes</p>\r\n<p>Turning Radius: 31&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>Optional Left or Right Hand Joystick: Yes</p>\r\n<p>Brake: Electro-Mechanical</p>\r\n<p>Top Speed: 4 mph</p>\r\n<p>Self-Diagnostic Warning Lights: Yes</p>\r\n<p>Battery Charge Distance: 15.2 miles</p>\r\n<p>Drive Type: 2 Motor Rear-Wheel Drive</p>\r\n<p>Grade Climbable: 8 degree</p>\r\n<p>Footplate: Large flip-up Footplate</p>\r\n<p>Adjustable Footplate: Yes, You can change the footplate vertically or horizontally</p>\r\n<p>Ground Clearance: 2.4&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>Seat Type: 18.5&rdquo; Swivel Captain Sea