x-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">FAQs</span></h6>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">How heavy is the Vive scooter?</span></h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\">The Vive mobility scooter weighs 88.2 pounds. The heaviest piece when disassembled for transportation is 29 pounds.</h6>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Can the Vive scooter make it over a 2&rdquo; doorstep?</span></h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\">The Vive scooter has a ground clearance of 1.57&rdquo; and will not be able to clear 2&rdquo; doorsteps.</h6>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">What type of battery does the scooter use?</span></h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\">The Vive scooter uses two, 12V/12AH batteries.</h6>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Can I drive through gravel with my Vive scooter?</span></h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Because gravel is uneven, the scooter is not recommended for gravel