nt-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Customers must report any issues with any product within the first 30 days of purchase. If any defects or damages at arrival are not reported within the first 30 days, the above warranties will not apply.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Noto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Any products that may come into contact with bodily fluids are not able to be returned when opened due to health risks. Products include but are not limited to bathroom safety, braces, mattresses, pads, cushions. Any item that falls under one of these categories will be reviewed using a predetermined set of formal requests and documentations before having the potential to qualify as returnable. This policy is in place for the health and well being of our employees, thank you for understanding.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-si